high_descs: Walk forward to the counter, then turn right and walk to the shelves on the right side against the wall.
Pick up the bowl off of the top shelf.
Turn right, then walk toward the counter and turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Place the bowl on the second shelf from the top of the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it back out.
Turn left, walk toward the door and turn right and go back to the shelves.
Put the bowl on the top shelf back in its original position.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled bowl on a shelf in the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn right, left and then turn right again and walk to the shelves.
Pick up the bowl from the shelves.
Turn right, then left to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the bowl in the fridge for a little bit and then take it out.
Turn left and walk around the corner back to the shelves.
Set the bowl on the shelves again.
anns.task_desc: Chill the bowl and set it back on the shelves.

high_descs: turn right and head towards the shelf
pick up a glass bowl from the shelf
turn right and locate the fridge
place the glass bowl to cool for some time in the fridge and then take it out
turn left and locate the shelf
place the glass bowl on the shelf
anns.task_desc: place a cold glass bowl on the shelf
